title: Switzerland 2 Year Note Yield
description: Switzerland 2Y Bond Yield was 0.57 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Switzerland 2 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 2.95 in June of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for Switzerland 2Y Bond Yield.
